               <code codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" code="44425-7" displayName="STORAGE AND HANDLING SECTION"/>
               <title>STORAGE</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Keep tightly closed. Store at controlled room temperature 15°-30°C (59°-86°F). Protect from light.</paragraph>
